        <num>CCP 3545</num>
        <heading>3545.  Nonresident attachment; venue</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 3545.  Nonresident attachment; venue
An action in which a writ of attachment is sought on the sole ground that the defendant is a nonresident may be brought in any parish where the property to be attached is situated.</p>
        </content>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
